  [$MEUSERPATH(5)]($MEUSERPATH(5)), [emf(8)](emf(8)), [erf(8)](erf(8)), [esf(8)](esf(8)), [$home(5)]($home(5)), emacs(1) [GNU], more(1),
  [Client-Server Interface](Client-Server(2)), [Command Line Filters](Command Line Filters).

