  [compare-windows(2)](compare-windows(2)), [compile(3)](compile(3)), [gdiff(3)](gdiff(3)), [xgrep(3)](xgrep(3)), [%xgrep-com(5)](%xgrep-com(5)),
  [xdiff(3)](xdiff(3)), [%xdiff-com(5)](%xdiff-com(5)).
