  [compare-windows(2)](compare-windows(2)), [compile(3)](compile(3)), diff(1), [gdiff(3f)](gdiff(3f)), [xgrep(3)](xgrep(3)),
  [%xgrep-com(5)](%xgrep-com(5)).
