  [Variable Functions](Introduction to Variable Functions), [&sin(4)](&sin(4)), [&slower(4)](&slower(4)), [&rep(4)](&rep(4)), [&add(4)](&add(4)), [&equal(4)](&equal(4)),
  [&cond(4)](&cond(4)), [Regular Expressions](RegularExpressions(2)).
