  me32.ini - Microsoft Window's Initialization (ini) File


## SYNOPSIS


  __;__ _Comments commence with a semi-colon_  

  __[Location]__  
  __exe__=_<executablePathname>_  

  __[Defaults]__  
  __meinstallpath=___<directoryPath>_;_<directoryPath>_; ... ;_<directoryPath>_  
